Package: kneedle
Title: Kneedle Algorithm; detecting knees in graphs
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Emmet", "Tam", , "emmet_tam@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The kneedle algorithm described in https://raghavan.usc.edu/papers/kneedle-simplex11.pdf composes
	 the main functionality of this package. It finds the maximal point of inflection within discrete data.
